snippet.title: Guntastic - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
WISHLIST IT NOW! 🕹️ 🤩 https://store.steampowered.com/app/981630/Guntastic/

Guntastic is an arcade-ish game involving shooting, mayhem, gore and yelling. Battle with up to four local or online players in incredibly fast, one-shot one-kill, non-stop matches over levels changing every few rounds.

Website https://playguntastic.com
Discord https://discord.gg/DNNbHc9
Twitter https://twitter.com/weareludicrous
